sub_title: Data Engineer | Artificial Intelligence (Honours) Graduate, Amsterdam and Singapore
summary:
A recent AI graduate and current Data Engineer / MSc. AI/Data Science student who aims to become a well-rounded data professional. 

My technical skillset includes:
-Python 
-SQL
-ELT pipelines
-Docker containerisation
-Data Build Tool (dbt)
-Apache Airflow
-Data modelling
-Customer Data Platform
-Machine Learning (esp. NLP, Knowledge Graphs) 
-Apache Beam

Also, I'm able to legally work in both the Netherlands and Singapore!
